"kepubify converts EPUB to KEPUB on the fly, which gives the Kobo accurate"
" reading-position tracking. Colophon will auto-download a pinned release "
"on the first book download. If the download fails, books are served as "
"raw EPUB (still readable, just less precise position tracking)."
